                        <a href="http://www.tescomobile.com">Home</a> <span class='breadcrumb__separator'>></span> <a href="http://www.tescomobile.com/about-us/">About us</a> <span class='breadcrumb__separator'>></span> <a href="http://www.tescomobile.com/about-us/terms-and-conditions/">Terms and Conditions</a> <span class='breadcrumb__separator'>></span> <a href="http://www.tescomobile.com/about-us/terms-and-conditions/general/">General</a> <span class='breadcrumb__separator'>></span> <span class="last">Privacy and Cookies Policy</span>
